{
  "texts": [
    "This dataset is based on the psycho-visual methodology employed by doctors during endoscopic examinations.",
    "A total of 196 ETIS-LARIB images have been included in the testing dataset, out of which only 156 images have been used for training with a resolution of 384x384 pixels.",
    "The CVC-ClinicDB database was created in association with the Hospital Clinic of Barcelona, Spain introduced by Bernal et al.",
    "To create CVC-ClinicDB, 23 separate video studies were combined with white light.",
    "Across all research studies, all sequences containing a polyp were retrieved, resulting in 31 sequences, each containing a unique polyp (Fig. 21)."
  ]
}